import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack} from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Section4 = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container maxW="1364px" h="1000px" bg="green.500">
                <Stack direction="row" spacing="100px" justify='center'>
                    <Box pt="300px">
                        <Stack direction="column" spacing="30px">
                            <Box w="416px" h="53px"  bg="yellow.200">
                                1
                            </Box>
                            <Box w="493px" h="189px" bg="gray.50">
                                2
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                    <Box pt="150px">
                        <Box w="589px" h="661px" bg="yellow.200">
                            <Image src="/Section/section4.png" />
                        </Box>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Section4
